4475b338c173496915546f522","tid":878402,"uid":14548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de1afe1adc81d191e7addabbc73f908fae5c860c","tid":878402,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"同期嘅德儀係技術係好鳩通，但可惜敵唔過鳩通嘅專利迫害，退出唔做電話u，認真可惜。<br />\n申：有用GN"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"高通真係害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"由Cdma開始  到3gwcdma 4G時代<br />\n一直帶住龍頭 個堆專利費收到fat fat<br />\n<br />\n曾經nokia  ericsson聯手告高通  最終輸<br />\n<br />\n5g應該又收一筆  nokia都有賺<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180823002333-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180823002333-260412&d=ohugl7sx8BWB9kVPH%2BgyFEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=18e31372\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180823002333-260412</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"依家5g 嘅餅仔係點分布？"},{"pid":"8c6ac676f8a4082ffb36e6b61e36d503ef06b651","tid":878402,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"歐洲專利局的有關於5G的專利出爐，其中華為5G專利數一共是1481，占比達到了28.90%，排在第二名的是愛立信公司，占比達到了22.13%，之後再是三星。<br />\n而統計全球的有關於5G的專利數量，中國廠商華為、中興等國產廠商一共擁有5G約30%的專利，高通一家擁有15%的專利，三星擁有18%，然後愛立信擁有13%左右，諾基亞也擁有11%左右，其餘的專利就分散在不同的廠商手中。<br />\n當然這只是專利數量，但從專利質量來看，理論上高通最高，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然高通只占有15%的專利，但估計核心專利最多，即標準必要專利數最多，因為在增強移動寬頻（eMBB）」場景中，高通主推的 LDPC 碼為數據信道編碼，自然它的核心專利數也最多</span>"},{"pid":"36b7df34856e9c395e96d65b1f07b4d966e55605","tid":878402,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.saowen.com/a/9fd8a8af64b1b6179155d350e106182c6c4cd963d4da99d2ca8ea9a1a7ebbe4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.saowen.com%2Fa%2F9fd8a8af64b1b6179155d350e106182c6c4cd963d4da99d2ca8ea9a1a7ebbe4c&d=ohugl7sx8BWB9kVPH%2BgyFEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d6fc3a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.saowen.com/a/9fd8a8af64b1b6179155d350e106182c6c4cd963d4da99d2ca8ea9a1a7ebbe4c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/191532_277fd609c5f5a7a6410a1b3fb620b58e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F191532_277fd609c5f5a7a6410a1b3fb620b58e.jpg&h=867efc25&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}